 loaded the input workbook, read data from the three source sheets, built a set of retired keys, combined rows from Existing Task and Additions while excluding any retired entries, and wrote the resulting rows into the Consolidated Tracker sheet starting at row 3. The workbook was saved to the output directory. Now we will verify the contents of the Consolidated Tracker sheet to ensure the correct rows were written, and then submit the final output spreadsheet path.
